# jText files to track for vendoring into ts_store
# Paths relative to the jText sibling root.
# The Sync_dependencies.sh script uses this list.
#
# When vendoring:
# - Most files are copied preserving structure under vendor/jText/
# - Files under src/tool/ are copied to vendor/jText/CLI/ (as per project convention)

